{"tid":385428,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MBC明日起大規模罷工  抗議打壓新聞自由","createTime":"2017-09-03T08:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T10:11:23.000Z","uid":37554,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0105f9cd863c2f801b3fd1c28073b862728b4a15","tid":385428,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:17:56.000Z","msg":"韓國MBC電視台工會因不滿內部有黑名單，員工因政治立場不同而被劃分等級，因此工會決定於明日開始大規模罷工，當中《無限挑戰》、《我獨自生活》等人氣綜藝節目亦因罷工而於本周起無限期停播。<br />\n<br />\n今次參與罷工嘅唔止節目組工作人員，連飯堂員工亦參與罷工，今次亦係MBC飯堂首次參與支持罷工，明日開始將停止供應餐飲。<br />\n而KBS電視台是次跟MBC一齊發起罷工，當中KBS晚間新聞亦將由平日嘅一小時，縮至40分鐘、周末晚間新聞由40分鐘縮至20分鐘。"},{"pid":"08c8e73c6dcc7ffddccfe27f4b12bc0bcb70a4b1","tid":385428,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/08/31/99/3943536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F99%2F3943536.jpg&h=114e6a5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5bb3eb2c06bc899cb203653dabd8151797bf473","tid":385428,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/08/31/99/3943538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F99%2F3943538.jpg&h=04c4786c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcafba72122089be23183de5bfd87282dc17d3cc","tid":385428,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d14aff9a3b4c63ed18a843fbc77e4df71d1360","tid":385428,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"有無人知港豬成日話&quot;其實仲有好多良心員工&quot;嘅TVB咁多年搞過乜"},{"pid":"08f3b3c1404a8cb330381884878d0a46e7778505","tid":385428,"uid